  "title": "Senior Facilities Maintenance Technician | Gross up to $5k/month | Shift work | Central - lq",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Central (Nearest MRT: Steven MRT) <br>\n<strong>Salary:</strong> Up to $5,500 (gross)<br>\n<strong>Work Schedule:</strong> Shift Work – 2 days, 2 nights, 2 off (12-hour shifts)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Duties: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform hands-on troubleshooting and repair of M&amp;E systems to ensure smooth building operations</li>\n  <li>Plan, execute, and supervise facilities maintenance and related services</li>\n  <li>Manage and coordinate M&amp;E installations, servicing, and preventive maintenance</li>\n  <li>Work closely with clients, contractors, and facilities teams to resolve technical issues</li>\n  <li>Prepare reports, quotations, and attend M&amp;E-related meetings as required</li>\n  <li>Maintain high standards of service quality and client relationships</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min Diploma in Engineering, Building, Real Estate, Facilities Management, or related field</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of relevant facilities maintenance experience preferred</li>\n  <li>Able to work on rotating shifts (day/night)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please submit your updated resume on Whatsapp at wa.me/6587504643 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Charlotte Loh Li Qin | Reg No.: R25127073</p>\n<p>Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA Licence No.: 23C1449</p>",
